settings.description: When were there so many pipes in the sky? Who knows, but for whatever reason Mario needs to get through all the piranhas and koopas.
There's gold inside these pyramids, if only I could figure out how to get inside.
Things get mysterious at night. Use pullied platforms and pipes to traverse piranhas and hot heads.
Darting amongst the clouds, you may find many interesting things, from Snake Blocks to Scales, with a Tanooki Suit to top it off, this long course will be sure to fulfill your Ace Coin Counter.
A recreation of 1-1 which is also a recreation of the e-Reader level

Solve puzzles, fill in empty spaces, set record time .. and play sudoku. Except it isn't sudoku? I'm baffled at what it's called. 

Hint: Make sure not to have a starman while getting a goomba's shoe.
World 1-1 from Super Mario Bros. Special.
This level has 5 ace coins and it has 250 sseconds, you need to defeat ludwig to end the level.

Vanquish the Palace of the Koopas as you dodge vicious traps and tricks!
